  "text": "For the automatic and offline analysis of the eye movement data, we used an in-house written program in MATLAB (MathWorks, Inc., Natick, MA). [CITATION_1] To pass quality control, at least 50% of centrifugal saccades needed to be acceptable for a participant to be included.",
